{Nightshade}

    Nightshade moved casually, her sensors had picked up a few energon
despoits but nothing she'd report...not at the moment at least, she'd get
some equipment and harvest the energon later herself. She continued moving
in range of the others scouting the land and the terrain keeping an eye out
for an area that would make a suitible secondary base for herself.
